      "roundness": null,
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "InferenceEngineDriver ABC\n\nCONTROL PLANE (via agent):\n• spawn(config) → SpawnResult\n• wait_healthy(config)\n• teardown(config, result)\n• is_running(config, result)\n\nDATA PLANE (direct to engine):\n• stream_prompt(prompt, run_id, params)\n  → AsyncIterator[str | ResponseMeta]\n\nUTILITIES:\n• health_url(config)\n• get_metrics_port(config)\n• validate_config(config)",
      "baseline": 164,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": "abc-box",
      "originalText": "InferenceEngineDriver ABC\n\nCONTROL PLANE (via agent):\n• spawn(config) → SpawnResult\n• wait_healthy(config)\n• teardown(config, result)\n• is_running(config, result)\n\nDATA PLANE (direct to engine):\n• stream_prompt(prompt, run_id, params)\n  → AsyncIterator[str | ResponseMeta]\n\nUTILITIES:\n• health_url(config)\n• get_metrics_port(config)\n• validate_config(config)",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "isDeleted": false
    },
