      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a13",
      "roundness": null,
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "FastAPI Agent (backend/agent.py) — runs on target host (localhost or Tailscale IP:8787)\n\nManaged mode only (spawn_mode=\"managed\"):\n  POST /spawn → starts engine subprocess, returns PID\n  GET /run/{run_id}/health → polls localhost:engine_port/health\n  GET /run/{run_id}/status → checks if process still alive\n  DELETE /run/{run_id} → kills engine subprocess\n\nAttach mode (spawn_mode=\"attach\"):\n  Agent NOT involved. Driver calls engine directly.",
      "baseline": 104,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": "agent-box",
      "originalText": "FastAPI Agent (backend/agent.py) — runs on target host (localhost or Tailscale IP:8787)\n\nManaged mode only (spawn_mode=\"managed\"):\n  POST /spawn → starts engine subprocess, returns PID\n  GET /run/{run_id}/health → polls localhost:engine_port/health\n  GET /run/{run_id}/status → checks if process still alive\n  DELETE /run/{run_id} → kills engine subprocess\n\nAttach mode (spawn_mode=\"attach\"):\n  Agent NOT involved. Driver calls engine directly.",
      "baseline": 104,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": "agent-box",
      "originalText": "FastAPI Agent (backend/agent.py) — runs on target host (localhost or Tailscale IP:8787)\n\nManaged mode only (spawn_mode=\"managed\"):\n  POST /spawn → starts engine subprocess, returns PID\n  GET /run/{run_id}/health → polls localhost:engine_port/health\n  GET /run/{run_id}/status → checks if process still alive\n  DELETE /run/{run_id} → kills engine subprocess\n\nAttach mode (spawn_mode=\"attach\"):\n  Agent NOT involved. Driver calls engine directly.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "isDeleted": false
    },
