      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "get_metrics_port(config) → int — tells orchestrator where sidecar should scrape\n\nOllama:     9091 (Python shim — no native /metrics, polls /api/ps)\nllama.cpp:  8080 (native /metrics)\nvLLM:       8000 (native /metrics)\nSGLang:     30000 (native /metrics)\n\nSidecar scrapes every N seconds, stamps run_id + engine + model labels, buffers, forwards to OTel Collector → VictoriaMetrics.",
      "baseline": 84,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": "metrics-box",
      "originalText": "get_metrics_port(config) → int — tells orchestrator where sidecar should scrape\n\nOllama:     9091 (Python shim — no native /metrics, polls /api/ps)\nllama.cpp:  8080 (native /metrics)\nvLLM:       8000 (native /metrics)\nSGLang:     30000 (native /metrics)\n\nSidecar scrapes every N seconds, stamps run_id + engine + model labels, buffers, forwards to OTel Collector → VictoriaMetrics.",
      "baseline": 84,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": "metrics-box",
      "originalText": "get_metrics_port(config) → int — tells orchestrator where sidecar should scrape\n\nOllama:     9091 (Python shim — no native /metrics, polls /api/ps)\nllama.cpp:  8080 (native /metrics)\nvLLM:       8000 (native /metrics)\nSGLang:     30000 (native /metrics)\n\nSidecar scrapes every N seconds, stamps run_id + engine + model labels, buffers, forwards to OTel Collector → VictoriaMetrics.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "isDeleted": false
    },
