      "roundness": null,
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "LOCAL EXECUTION (host=localhost, spawn_mode=managed)\n\n1. execute_run() calls driver.spawn(config)\n   → driver POSTs to http://localhost:8787/spawn\n   → agent subprocess engine, returns PID\n2. driver.wait_healthy(config)\n   → driver POSTs to http://localhost:8787/run/{run_id}/health\n   → agent checks localhost:engine_port/health\n3. run benchmark — driver.stream_prompt() calls \n   → http://localhost:engine_port/v1/completions (direct, no agent)",
      "baseline": 104,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": "flow-local",
      "originalText": "LOCAL EXECUTION (host=localhost, spawn_mode=managed)\n\n1. execute_run() calls driver.spawn(config)\n   → driver POSTs to http://localhost:8787/spawn\n   → agent subprocess engine, returns PID\n2. driver.wait_healthy(config)\n   → driver POSTs to http://localhost:8787/run/{run_id}/health\n   → agent checks localhost:engine_port/health\n3. run benchmark — driver.stream_prompt() calls \n   → http://localhost:engine_port/v1/completions (direct, no agent)",
      "baseline": 104,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": "flow-local",
